text: Enoch Kelly Haney (November 12, 1940 â€“ April 23, 2022) was an American Democratic politician and artist. He was principal chief of the Seminole Nation of Oklahoma from 2005 until 2009 and was a member of both houses of the Oklahoma Legislature from 1980 until 2022.Seminole Nation Executive Branch- Principal Chief Enoch Kelly Haney He was also a candidate for Governor of Oklahoma in the 2002 election. Haney was born in Seminole, Oklahoma. Haney died on April 23, 2022 in Oklahoma City, Oklahoma at the age of 81. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:2022 deaths Category:American artists Category:Politicians from Oklahoma Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
